name: Roy Tang
text: /puts on comic book guy hat. Walang namatay sa Killing Joke. You probably mean Jason Todd being killed by Joker in the 80s, but nonlethal pa rin sya all the way. When Jason got rezzed two decades later, it was part of why he was angry with Bruce - pinatay na sya at lahat pero buhay pa din si Joker
